com.exlibris.dps.sdk.registry

Interface PublisherRegistryPlugin


  • public interface PublisherRegistryPlugin
    Interface for a publisherRegistry plug-in type. The plugin manages the publish and unPublish actions on a converted IE. The conversion may be done by a ConverterRegistryPlugin plug-in type.
    This plugin interface only supports java implementation.
